Package: SVMCwebr
Title: SVMC Allocation Model for WebR
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("HAMK", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "olli.niemitalo@hamk.fi"),
    person("Hui", "Tang", role = "aut",
           comment = "Original SVMC Fortran code (huitang-earth/SVMC)")
    )
Description: WebR-compatible R wrapper for the SVMC (Simple Vegetation Model of
    Carbon) allocation submodel. Provides R-callable interfaces to the Fortran
    allocation subroutines (alloc_hypothesis_2, invert_alloc) for browser-based
    comparison with the jax-js-nonconsuming TypeScript port. The Fortran source
    derives from vendor/SVMC with minimal modifications for R compatibility
    (see src/allocation.f90 header).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
